        <item>
            <title>中国研发全球最快四足机械人，秒速 10 米媲美「飞人」保特</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/15/fastest-4-leg-robot-dog-from-china-10ms/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fastest-4-leg-robot-dog-from-china-10ms</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/15/fastest-4-leg-robot-dog-from-china-10ms/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[四足机械人]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286724</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>浙江大学杭州国际科创中心人形机械人创新研究院、镜识科技有限公司及杭州凯达尔焊接机械人股份有限公司联手，成功研发出全球最快的四足机械人「黑豹 2.0」，其奔跑速度达每秒 10 米，可媲美短跑名将保特。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286837" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/62694ae2295745a68805-694x377.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/62694ae2295745a68805-694x377.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/62694ae2295745a68805.jpeg 822w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/824/539.htm">IT 之家</a></p><p>「黑豹 2.0」重 38 公斤，站立高度达 0.63 米。研发团队以动力学为基础，参考黑豹与跳鼠等动物的运动特征，提升机械人的髋关节、膝关节及足部设计，提升其强度、韧性和精度。据中国媒体《新浪》报道，「黑豹 2.0」是全球跑得最快的「四足机械人」，最高速度可达 10 米每秒，可媲美全球短跑纪录保持者保特，保特以 9.58 秒跑毕 100 米。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286838" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/6fa73ed76d014d9e89a8-694x392.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/6fa73ed76d014d9e89a8-694x392.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/6fa73ed76d014d9e89a8.jpeg 819w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲时速可达 10 米每秒，图片来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/824/539.htm">IT 之家</a></p><p>为令「黑豹 2.0」可高速奔跑，开发团队运用了惠更斯耦合摆原理，令「黑豹 2.0」四足协调运动，可以合力快速冲刺。膝关节内置弹簧作为缓冲装置，减少高速运动中对地面的冲击与能耗。为解决高速奔跑时小腿易断的问题，研发人员设计了模仿跳鼠结构的碳纤维小腿，虽然重量增加 16%，但坚硬度提升了 135%。此外，特制的「跑鞋」提升了抓地性能，增幅达 200%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/small_20250114150413.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="301" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲模仿跳鼠结构的碳纤维小腿，图片来源：<a href="https://www.gamersky.com/tech/202501/1871288.shtml">GamerSky</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286841" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/small_20250114150414.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="304" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.gamersky.com/tech/202501/1871288.shtml">GamerSky</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286847" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011435659-694x411.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011435659-694x411.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011435659.jpg 1042w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲特制「跑鞋」提升抓地性能，图片来源：<a href="https://www.gamersky.com/tech/202501/1871288.shtml">GamerSky</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/roll/2025-01-14/doc-ineexptx8669466.shtml">Sina</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
